(1987)<p>
<a name="c55"><a href="#~c55">(55)</a> <i>Smith v. Gore,</i> 728 SW 2nd 738
(1987)<p>

<a name="c56"><a href="#~c56">(56)</a> <i>Parens
Patriae:</i> "Father of his country; parent of the country. In England,
