<li><a href="mailto:gpph16a@prodigy.com>Atlanta Journal-Constitution</a>
  (Specify in message whom it is for.)
<li>Austin (TX) American-Statesman
  <ul>
  <li><a href="mailto:letters@statesman.com">Letter to the Editor</a>
  <li><a href="mailto:news@statesman.com">News Editor</a>
  <li><a href="mailto:business@statesman.com">Business Editor</a>
  <li><a href="mailto:features@statesman.com">Features Editor</a>
  <li><a href="mailto:sports@statesman.com">Sports Editor</a>
  <li><a href="mailto:xlent@statesman.com">Arts and Entertainment Editor</a>
  </ul>
