<h3>Disclaimers</h3>

This list was originally assembled by Adam G. &#160,
<a href="mailto:adamg@world.std.com">adamg@world.std.com</a>,
under the title "The Media List: The Whole Thing",
HTML version by Tim DeRyan,
<a href="mailto:webs@inet1.inetworld.net">webs@inet1.inetworld.net</a>.
Additional addresses from
<a href="mailto:newslink@ix.netcom.com">Bob Venverloh</a>.
Modified to fit our "style" by Ohio Right to Life.<p>

In any list of this size, there are bound to be errors. If you find one,
please let us know and we will fix it as soon as possible. If you find any
additional media addresses, please let us know about that, too.<p>

