Some concerns have been raised about our publishing people's addresses
without first getting their approval. Therefore, we are revising this
list to only
include those who have specifically asked or agreed to be on it. In the
near
future we hope to contact everyone who used to be on the list. If your
Right to Life organization would like to be on, please write to
<a href="mailto:life@ohiolife.org">us</a> and we'll add you.<p>

In the mean time, if you'd like to get in contact with pro-lifers in your area,
call National Right to Life at 202-626-8800 ext 129 for assistance.

