<hr>
<font size=-1>Note 1: Information in this list comes from a variety of sources,
and we cannot guarantee that it is current or accurate. Corrections, additions,
and deletions are welcome.<p>

Note 2: Right to Life does not necessarily support or endorse any of these
organizations, nor do we always agree with their policies. Inclusion on this
list means that it is our understanding that the organization is pro-life, and
that's all it means.</font>
<hr>

