<DOCNO>WT22-B39-75</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA084-000600-B044-160</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ohiolife.org:80/qa/qa18.htm 206.103.235.236 19970216072954 text/html 20103
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 16 Feb 1997 07:30:11 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
