<title>Foreword - The Moral Question of Abortion</title>
</head>

<BODY bgcolor=669999>

<!-- Container -->
<CENTER>

<TABLE BGCOLOR=669999 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 WIDTH=620 BORDER=0>
