<FONT COLOR=000000>
.
</FONT>
</TD>

<TD WIDTH=570 BGCOLOR=CCCCCC ALIGN=left VALIGN=middle>
	<TABLE BGCOLOR=CCCCCC CELLPADDING=15 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0>
	<TR><TD>
	<FONT COLOR=Black Size=3>
	<STRONG>
	Chapter 2: Is Abortion the Killing of this Being?<BR>
	</STRONG>
	<TABLE><TR><TD WIDTH=20></TD><TD>
	<FONT Size=2>
	Methods of Abortion - 
	<A HREF=2-2.htm>Abortion a Form of Infanticide?</A> - 
	<A HREF=2-3.htm>Is Abortion Murder?</A> -
	<A HREF=2-4.htm>Abortions Resulting in Live Births</A>
	</TD></TR></TABLE>

	</TD></TR>
	</TABLE>
