	<TR><TD>
	<FONT COLOR=Black Size=3>
	<STRONG>
	<A HREF=2-1.htm>Chapter 2: Is Abortion the Killing of this Being?</A><BR>
	</STRONG>
	<TABLE><TR><TD WIDTH=20></TD><TD>
	<FONT Size=2>
	<A HREF=2-1.htm>Methods of Abortion</A> - 
	<A HREF=2-2.htm>Abortion a Form of Infanticide?</A> - 
	<A HREF=2-3.htm>Is Abortion Murder?</A> -
	Abortions Resulting in Live Births
	</TD></TR></TABLE>

