<title>Chapter 3: Does Abortion Cause Pain to its Victim?</title>
</head>

<BODY bgcolor=669999>

<!-- Container -->
<CENTER>

<TABLE BGCOLOR=669999 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 WIDTH=620 BORDER=0>
